{
  "page": "House Allyrion",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold\">House Allyrion of Godsgrace</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Allyrion.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Allyrion.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a6/House_Allyrion.svg/250px-House_Allyrion.svg.png\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a6/House_Allyrion.svg/375px-House_Allyrion.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a6/House_Allyrion.svg/500px-House_Allyrion.svg.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"width:100%;min-width:300px;position:relative;z-index:100;border:0 grey solid;margin-top:-2em;margin-bottom:0.5em;\"><div style=\"display: table; width: calc(100% - 80px); height: 28px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 12px; margin: 0px auto 0px; padding: 0;border:0; position: relative; border-collapse:collapse; text-align: center; font-family: &#39;Uncial Antiqua&#39;; color: #fd0; background: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, #700 0, #700 25%, #333 25%, #333 50%);\">\n  <div style=\"display:table-cell; vertical-align: middle; padding: 4px; clip-path: polygon(2px 2px, calc(100% - 2px) 2px, calc(100% - 2px) calc(100% - 2px), 2px calc(100% - 2px)); background: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, #a00 0, #a00 25%, #000 25%, #000 50%);\">No Foe May Pass</div>\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top: -14px; width: 56px; height: 28px; z-index: -3; left: -42px; clip-path: polygon(calc(100% - 2px) calc(100% - 2px), 5px calc(100% - 2px), calc(25% + 3px) 50%, 5px 2px, calc(100% - 2px) 2px, 75% 50%, calc(100% - 2px) calc(100% - 2px), calc(100% - 2px) 5px, calc(75% + 3px) 50%); background: #000;\"></div>\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top: -14px; width: 56px; height: 28px; z-index: -4; left: -42px; clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0% 100%, 25% 50%); background: #333;\"></div>\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top: -14px; width: 56px; height: 28px; z-index: -3; right: -42px; clip-path: polygon(2px calc(100% - 2px), calc(100% - 5px) calc(100% - 2px), calc(75% - 3px) 50%, calc(100% - 5px) 2px, 2px 2px, 25% 50%, 2px calc(100% - 2px), 2px 5px, calc(25% - 3px) 50%); background: #a00;\"></div>\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top: -14px; width: 56px; height: 28px; z-index: -4; right: -42px; clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 75% 50%, 100% 100%, 0% 100%); background: #700;\"></div></div></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Coat of arms</th><td>\nA golden hand on gyronny red and black<br />(<i>Gyronny gules and sable, a hand or</i>)</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Seat</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Godsgrace\" title=\"Godsgrace\">Godsgrace</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Head</th><td>\nLady <a href=\"/index.php/Delonne_Allyrion\" title=\"Delonne Allyrion\">Delonne Allyrion</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Region</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Godsgrace\" title=\"Lord of Godsgrace\">Lord of Godsgrace</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Heir</th><td>\nSer <a href=\"/index.php/Ryon_Allyrion\" title=\"Ryon Allyrion\">Ryon Allyrion</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Overlord</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\">House Martell</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Founded</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Coming_of_the_Andals\" title=\"Coming of the Andals\">Coming of the Andals</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>House Allyrion of Godsgrace</b> is a major <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dornish</a> noble house. <a href=\"/index.php/Godsgrace\" title=\"Godsgrace\">Godsgrace</a> sits near the confluence of the <a href=\"/index.php/Scourge\" title=\"Scourge\">Scourge</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Vaith_(river)\" title=\"Vaith (river)\">Vaith</a> into the <a href=\"/index.php/Greenblood\" title=\"Greenblood\">Greenblood</a>.\n</p><p>Their blazon is a golden hand on gyronny red and black.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Their words do not appear in the books, but according to semi-canon sources they are \"No Foe May Pass\".<sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#The_Winds_of_Winter\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#House_Allyrion_at_the_end_of_the_third_century\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">House Allyrion at the end of the third century</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Allyrion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>House Allyrion was founded by <a href=\"/index.php/Andal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal\">Andal</a> adventurers during the <a href=\"/index.php/Coming_of_the_Andals\" title=\"Coming of the Andals\">coming of the Andals</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a>, along with Houses <a href=\"/index.php/House_Jordayne\" title=\"House Jordayne\">Jordayne</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\">Martell</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Qorgyle\" title=\"House Qorgyle\">Qorgyle</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Santagar\" title=\"House Santagar\">Santagar</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Uller\" title=\"House Uller\">Uller</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Vaith\" title=\"House Vaith\">Vaith</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf793_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf793-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>House Martell was once a <a href=\"/index.php/Bannerman\" title=\"Bannerman\">vassal</a> to the Allyrions of <a href=\"/index.php/Godsgrace\" title=\"Godsgrace\">Godsgrace</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf793_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf793-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/First_Dornish_War\" title=\"First Dornish War\">First Dornish War</a>, the Allyrions fled their castle before the arrival of Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaenys_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaenys Targaryen\">Rhaenys Targaryen</a> on her <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragon</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Meraxes\" title=\"Meraxes\">Meraxes</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf31.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf31.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Allyrion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Allyrion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Ryon_Allyrion\" title=\"Ryon Allyrion\">Ryon Allyrion</a> and his bastard son, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_Sand\" title=\"Daemon Sand\">Daemon Sand</a>, are among the Dornish nobles who accompany Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Oberyn_Martell\" title=\"Oberyn Martell\">Oberyn Martell</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>. The Bastard of Godsgrace helps Oberyn don his armor before the duel against Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Gregor_Clegane\" title=\"Gregor Clegane\">Gregor Clegane</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Allyrion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Daemon is arrested by men in service to <a href=\"/index.php/Doran_Martell\" title=\"Doran Martell\">Doran Martell</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Prince_of_Dorne\" title=\"Prince of Dorne\">Prince of Dorne</a>, for demanding the release of the <a href=\"/index.php/Sand_Snakes\" title=\"Sand Snakes\">Sand Snakes</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Allyrion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>The Lord of Godsgrace<sup id=\"cite_ref-10\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-10\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup> is present at the feast when Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Balon_Swann\" title=\"Balon Swann\">Balon Swann</a> arrives in <a href=\"/index.php/Sunspear\" title=\"Sunspear\">Sunspear</a> to deliver the <a href=\"/index.php/Mountain%27s_skull\" title=\"Mountain&#39;s skull\">Mountain's skull</a>. He drinks when <a href=\"/index.php/Ricasso\" title=\"Ricasso\">Ricasso</a> raises a toast to King <a href=\"/index.php/Tommen_Baratheon\" title=\"Tommen Baratheon\">Tommen I Baratheon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Winds_of_Winter\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Allyrion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Winds of Winter\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #f28500;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Content.png\" src=\"/images/c/cc/Content.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Warning</b> <br /> This information has thus far been released in a sample chapter for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, and might therefore not be in finalized form. Keep in mind that the content as described below is still subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>Daemon comes from Godsgrace to Sunspear to be part of Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_Martell\" title=\"Arianne Martell\">Arianne Martell</a>'s party sent by her father, Prince Doran, to meet with <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_Targaryen_(Young_Griff)\" title=\"Aegon Targaryen (Young Griff)\">Aegon Targaryen</a>. He is named Arianne's <a href=\"/index.php/Sworn_shield\" title=\"Sworn shield\">sworn shield</a>. While sailing across the <a href=\"/index.php/Sea_of_Dorne\" title=\"Sea of Dorne\">Sea of Dorne</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Cape_Wrath\" title=\"Cape Wrath\">Cape Wrath</a>, Daemon defeats Arianne in a game of <i><a href=\"/index.php/Cyvasse\" title=\"Cyvasse\">cyvasse</a></i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwow.5B.5Barianne_i_.28the_winds_of_winter.29.7Carianne_i.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_12-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwow.5B.5Barianne_i_.28the_winds_of_winter.29.7Carianne_i.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-12\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"House_Allyrion_at_the_end_of_the_third_century\">House Allyrion at the end of the third century</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Allyrion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: House Allyrion at the end of the third century\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The known Allyrions during the timespan of the events described in <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i> are:\n</p>\n<ul><li>Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Delonne_Allyrion\" title=\"Delonne Allyrion\">Delonne Allyrion</a>, the Lady of Godsgrace.\n<ul><li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Ryon_Allyrion\" title=\"Ryon Allyrion\">Ryon Allyrion</a>, her son and heir.\n<ul><li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_Sand\" title=\"Daemon Sand\">Daemon Sand</a>, Ryon's bastard son. Known as the Bastard of Godsgrace.</li>\n<li>Ryon's two sons by <a href=\"/index.php/Ynys_Yronwood\" title=\"Ynys Yronwood\">Ynys Yronwood</a>, his wife.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_13-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-13\">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></li></ul></li></ul>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Delonne_Allyrion\" title=\"Delonne Allyrion\">Delonne</a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Unknown<br />husband</td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td></tr><tr align=\"center\"><td style=\"border-right:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td><div style=\"width:1em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td></tr>\n<tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border-right:1px solid b